Local Functions (/std/inheritables/living.c)

void add_skill_points(string skill,int x);

Adds points to a given skill.  Once the points are high enough this function automaticlly promotes the skill to the next level.

See also: use_skill(), add_skill_adj_points(), set_skills(), set_skill(), query_skills(), query_skill_level(), query_skill_max(), query_base_skill(), set_skill_bonus(), add_skill_bonus(), query_skill_bonus(), add_skill_points()
